'''Eʋeviwo''', woakekeŋ wova tso [[Nɔtse]].  Nyitso didi, fia [[Agɔkɔli]] nɔ Nɔtse.  Amewo kekeŋ, wonɔ Nɔtse le xɔme. Amewo dibe woadzo, gake fia gbe. Gbesiagbe, nyɔnuwo klɔ agbawo kple wonya awuwo.  Etsi ke kpɔtɔ, wo tsɔe ƒugbe le xɔŋti. Ekpɔtɔ vide, xɔ gbãŋ. Eʋeviwo tso. Woyi kpata kpata - [[Ghana]], [[Togo]], kple [[Benin]].  Ameadewo yi [[Atakpame]] kple amebubuawo yi Lome kple Anexɔ.  Fifia, Eʋeviwo le sigbe 2.000.000 nene.


Eʋeawo katã wo dzɔ tso Nɔtse. Woƒe fia si nɔ dziɖum la ŋkoe nye Tɔgbe Agɔkɔli. Wotɔ gli-kpɔ ga aɖe ƒoxla Nɔtse du blibo la kata. Alesi fia la nye ŋutasela ta la, dumeviawo kata ɖoe kplikpa be ye woasi adzo le fia la gbɔ. Le esiata la, wo ɖoe na nyɔnuwo be woa nɔ tsi ƒom ɖe gli-kpɔ la ŋu ɣesiaɣi si woanyanu alo aklɔ agbame. Esia yi edzi vaseɖe esime gli-kpɔ la gba eye Eʋeawo to gli-kpɔ gbagba la me si le fia vɔɖi Tɔgbe Agɔkɔli gbɔ yi ɖe Ghana, Benin kple Togo ƒe teƒe bubuwo. Le fifia me la, Eʋeawo anɔ abe ame 2,000,000 ene,

